data.title: Martin Sheen and Emilio Estevez bring star power to Edmonds
data.meta_description: The father-and-son duo of Martin Sheen and Emilio Estevez turned heads and stopped traffic on Main Street in Edmonds Monday during an hours-long promotional shoot with Rick Steves for the rerelease  …
